1. Ovo je bilo veoma *neugodno* iskustvo. (This was a very *unpleasant* experience.)
2. Ne bih voleo da se ponovi *neugodan* incident od prošle nedelje. (I wouldn't like the *unpleasant* incident from last week to happen again.)
3. Čudno je kako neki ljudi uživaju u *neugodnim* situacijama. (It's strange how some people enjoy *unpleasant* situations.)
4. Molim te, nemoj da mi činiš *neugodnosti*. (Please don't cause me any *unpleasantness*.)
5. Osećam se veoma *neugodno* zbog toga što sam zakasnio na sastanak. (I feel very *uncomfortable* because I was late for the meeting.)
6. Nisam mogao da podnesem *neugodnu* tišinu koja je nastala nakon mog pitanja. (I couldn't bear the *awkward* silence that followed my question.)
7. Imam *neugodan* osećaj da nešto nije u redu. (I have an *uneasy* feeling that something is wrong.)
8. *Neugodno* me iznenadio tvoj izbor. (Your choice *surprised* me unpleasantly.)
9. Nije bilo ni malo *neugodno* izaći na scenu i predstaviti se publici. (It wasn't at all *unpleasant* to go out on stage and introduce myself to the audience.)
10. Iako mu je bilo *neugodno*, morao je priznati svoju grešku. (Although it was *embarrassing* for him, he had to admit his mistake.)